query:
SELECT team, SUM(overall) as total_overall, COUNT(*) as player_count 
FROM players 
WHERE team IS NOT NULL AND team != 'Free Agents'
GROUP BY team 
ORDER BY total_overall DESC 
LIMIT 10;
